This folder is where add-on clothing thumbnails live when using the
local image host (no external CDN).

Drop PNG files here manually, or use the orb-clothing_companion
importer to auto-populate from orb-greenscreen output.

Filename format: {model}-{prefix}-{drawable}.png

Examples:
    mp_m_freemode_01-torso_1-400.png
    mp_m_freemode_01-helmet_1-6.png
    mp_f_freemode_01-pants_1-155.png

After adding files, `restart orb-clothing` so FiveM re-scans the folder.

See orb-clothing_companion/SETUP.md for the full walkthrough.
